\begin_layout Subsection
The standard error
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
All estimators in this paper can be written as smooth functions of a finite collection of (possibly weighted) U-statistics and V-statistics.
Under pairwise MCAR, a joint central limit theorem holds for these statistics, and the delta method yields asymptotic covariance matrices for the corresponding kappa estimators.
\end_layout

